These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-2-1::.
House: victorian, gothic-revival, wooden, ranch-style, futuristic
City: edinburgh, nizza, liverpool, berlin, hamburg
1. the victorian house is on the far left##1
2. the victorian house is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
3. the ranch-style house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
4. the person traveling to liverpool is between the gothic-revival house and the person traveling to edinburgh##2
5. the ranch-style house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
6. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |         3          |    4     |      5      |
| House     | victorian | wooden | futuristic | ranch-style   | gothic-revival |
| City   | nizza   | hamburg    | edinburgh         | liverpool | berlin  |

