.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-2-2::.
There are 5 different nationalities: british, egyptian, french, russian, dutch
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: zinnia, orchid, amaryllis, tulip, daisy
1. the person who growstulip is the french##1
2. the egyptian is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
3. the person who growszinnia is in the middle##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is the russian##1
5. the british is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
6. the russian is between the french and the dutch##2
7. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |     3      |     4      |    5    |
| Nationality          | french | russian | dutch     | egyptian | british |
| Flower   | tulip | amaryllis | zinnia | orchid      | daisy  |

