.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-2-3::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: comedy, disaster, scientific, western, martial-arts
The people use 5 different means of transport: jet-ski, bike, helicopter, subway, scooter
1. the person watching scientific movies is between the person watching western movies and the person watching comedy movies##2
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
5. the person watching comedy movies is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person driving the bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |      2       |     3     |     4     |         5          |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | disaster     | comedy    | scientific | western              |
| Transport    | subway  | bike | helicopter | jet-ski  | scooter |

