.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-2-4::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, almond-milk, milk, water
The people use 5 different means of transport: train, jet-ski, airplane, snowmobile, boat
1. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the train##1
2. the person drinking water is the person drinking water##1
3. the person driving the airplane is the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person driving the train is between the person drinking 7up and the person driving the jet-ski##2
6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
7. the person drinking cola is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5     |
| Beverage          | 7up | almond-milk      | cola   | water | milk    |
| Transport   | airplane   | train | jet-ski | snowmobile | boat |

