.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-2-5::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, havana, montecristo, siglo, tiparillo
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: october, june, april, february, september
1. the havana-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
3. the cain-smoker is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person who's birthday is in october and the siglo-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |      2      |       3       |    4    |    5    |
| Cigar       | cain | havana | siglo | montecristo | tiparillo |
| Birthday   | october       | september         | february          | june     | april  |

