.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-2-6::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: camping, woodworking, baking, puzzles, traveling
5 different pets are kept: rat, horse, snake, fish, bird
1. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
4. the owner of the bird is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
5. the person who's hobby is camping is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the owner of the rat##2
6. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the horse and the person who's hobby is traveling##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1        |      2       |    3     |      4       |      5       |
| Hobby   | baking          | woodworking     | camping  | puzzles       | traveling       |
| Pet    | fish | rat | horse | bird | snake |

