.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-2-7::.
5 different pets are kept: fish, mouse, frog, pony, rabbit
5 different games are played: snooker, mah-jongg, billiard, whist, monopoly
1. the person playing whist is on the far right##1
2. the person playing monopoly is between the person playing mah-jongg and the owner of the pony##2
3. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the owner of the pony is the person playing snooker##1
5. the owner of the mouse is in the middle##1
6. the person playing whist is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
7. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
8. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |     5     |
| Pet           | frog    | fish | mouse   | pony | rabbit |
| Game   | billiard | mah-jongg    | monopoly | snooker | whist      |

