.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-2-8::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, bongani, montecristo, davidoff, siglo
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: funk, trance, r&b, techno, reggae
1. the fan reggae is between the davidoff-smoker and the fan trance##2
2. the fan r&b is the davidoff-smoker##1
3. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the fan techno##1
4. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
5. the oliveros-smoker is between the fan r&b and the bongani-smoker##2
6. the fan funk is on the far right##1
7. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the fan r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |     3      |      4      |   5    |
| Cigar         | siglo      | bongani  | oliveros | davidoff | montecristo |
| Music-Genre   | techno | trance | reggae       | r&b     | funk   |

