.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-2-12::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  fisherman, scientist, freelancer, engineer, writer
5 different games are played: monopoly, billiard, poker, whist, backgammon
1. the engineer is on the left of the writer##1
2. the fisherman is on the far left##1
3. the person playing backgammon is the fisherman##1
4. the fisherman is on the left of the freelancer##1
5. the person playing poker is on the right of the freelancer##1
6. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
7. the person playing poker is between the engineer and the person playing whist##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3    |     4      |     5     |
| Job          | fisherman   | freelancer | scientist | engineer | writer |
| Game   | backgammon | whist        | poker | billiard      | monopoly |

