5 different pets are kept: cat, mouse, fish, goldfish, bird
1. the owner of the fish is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
6. the owner of the cat is the person drinking coffee##1
7. the person drinking coffee is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the bird##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |      2       |      3      |     4      |   5    |
| Beverage         | 7up | coffee | soy-milk | tea | hot-chocolate |
| Pet   | fish | cat   | bird       | mouse  | goldfish   |

