.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-2-14::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: subway, roller, motorbike, trike, jet-ski
The people have 5 different hobbies: puzzles, fishing, hiking, singing, board-games
1. the person who's hobby is singing is the person driving the subway##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person driving the trike and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person driving the roller##1
5. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4     |     5      |
| Transport   | subway | motorbike     | jet-ski   | trike    | roller       |
| Hobby         | singing  | hiking | board-games | fishing | puzzles |

