.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-2-15::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: apricot, aquamarine, blue, fuchsia, brown
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, november, february, september, october
1. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who likes fuchsia##2
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
6. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |  4   |     5      |
| Color   | brown     | aquamarine | apricot | blue | fuchsia      |
| Birthday    | february | october     | september   | november | march |

