1. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
4. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
6. the person playing whist is between the person playing bridge and the person playing go##2
7. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |      2      |       3       |   4    |    5    |
| Birthday   | march  | august | may | september  | july     |
| Game      | backgammon | bridge       | whist     | go | snooker |

