.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-2-19::.
There 5 different types of food: pomegranate, orange, pineapple, lettuce, onion
There are 5 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea, 7up, water, lemonade
1. the person eating pomegranate is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person eating orange is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person eating onion##1
6. the person eating onion is between the person drinking tea and the person eating pineapple##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |        3        |     4      |     5     |
| Food           | pineapple  | onion | lettuce | orange   | pomegranate |
| Beverage   | lemonade | water   | tea         | hot-chocolate | 7up |

