.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-2-20::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: surfing, golf, weightlifting, skiing, soccer
The people have 5 different jobs:  doctor, manager, software-developer, electrician, architect
1. the doctor is on the far left##1
2. the architect is on the right of the software-developer##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing is the electrician##1
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the electrician##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
6. the electrician is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who's sport is golf##2
7. the software-developer is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |       2       |   3    |     4      |  5   |
| Sport   | golf | skiing | surfing | weightlifting      | soccer |
| Job        | doctor | electrician       | manager    | software-developer | architect  |

 